<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>My Windows dev box doesn't have sqlite enabled in php.ini.</p>

<p>When running the unit tests, they stop at line 35 of tests\Zend\Cache\SqliteBackendTest :
        $this-&gt;_instance = new Zend_Cache_Backend_Sqlite(array(
            'cacheDBCompletePath' =&gt; $this-&gt;_cacheDir . 'cache.db'
        ));</p>

<p>There is no error message given, the phpunit script just dies:</p>

<p>$ phpunit.bat AllTests.php<br />
